    <Placemark>
      <name>Tempura Yamanoue Roppongi</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Tempura Yamanoue Roppongi</strong><br/>Tokyo / Akasaka<br/>Address: 3F, Tokyo Midtown Galleria Garden Terrace, 9-7-4, Akasaka, Minato-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: Directly connected to the underground passage of Roppongi Station on the Tokyo Metro Hibiya Line; Directly connected to the 8th exit of Roppongi Station on the Toei Oedo Line.; A 3-minute walk from Nogizaka Station on the Tokyo Metro Chiyoda Line<br/>Cuisine: Tempura<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 25,000 - 30,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 16,000 - 22,000<br/>Summary: Inheriting the spirit and tradition of the legendary Tempura Yamanoue, this Tokyo Midtown restaurant showcases the traditional flavors of tempura to connoisseurs from around the world.<br/>Signature cues: Tempura<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244993/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>139.730151,35.666187,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>XEX ATAGO GREEN HILLS</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>XEX ATAGO GREEN HILLS</strong><br/>Tokyo / Atago<br/>Address: 42F, Atago Green Hills MORI Tower, 2-5-1, Atago, Minato-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: A 4-minutes walk from Toei Mita Line Onarimon Station Exit A5; A 5-minute walk from exit 3 of Kamiyacho Station on the Tokyo Metro Hibiya Line<br/>Cuisine: Italian<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Dinner: JPY 11,550 - 27,500<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 6,380 - 8,250<br/>Child policy: Weekends: elementary school students and above. Weekdays: junior high school students and above are welcome<br/>Summary: Enjoy a panoramic view of Tokyo from the 42nd floor while indulging in a luxurious hideaway for adults.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/245065/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
      <Point>
        <coordinates>139.749031,35.662123,0</coordinates>
      </Point>
