      <name>Kuriyagawa</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Kuriyagawa</strong><br/>Tokyo / Ebisu<br/>Address: 1F, 4-23-10, Ebisu, Shibuya-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: 8-minute walk from Ebisu station, Hibiya Line<br/>Cuisine: Sushi<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 22,000 - 40,700<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 9,900 - 40,700<br/>Summary: The chef at this sushi restaurant creates dishes that respect the traditions of edomae sushi whilst adding elements of playfulness to create a fresh sensation.<br/>Signature cues: Sushi<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/243927/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
