      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Ebisu Unagi Matsukawa</strong><br/>Tokyo / Ebisuminami<br/>Address: 2-21-7, Ebisuminami, Shibuya-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: 5-minute walk from Ebisu station east exit on the JR Yamanote Line<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$ Under JPY 10k<br/>Dinner: JPY 9,500 - 16,000<br/>Lunch range: $$ JPY 5k-10k<br/>Lunch: JPY 5,500 - 8,800<br/>Summary: Customers are able to enjoy luxurious courses of Mariboshi, or &quot;dream eel&quot;, at this high class and relaxing space.<br/>Signature cues: Kaiseki<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244327/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
