      <name>Takumi Sushi Owana</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Takumi Sushi Owana</strong><br/>Tokyo / Ebisuminami<br/>Address: 4F, TIMEZONE Terrace Building, 1-17-17, Ebisuminami, Shibuya-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: A 3-minute walk from Ebisu Station, Exit 1(Tokyo Metro Hibiya Line); A 3-minute walk from Ebisu Station Exit West(JR Yamanote Line)<br/>Cuisine: Sushi<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$$$ JPY 30k+<br/>Dinner: JPY 30,000 - 30,000<br/>Lunch range: $$$$ JPY 20k+<br/>Lunch: JPY 30,000 - 30,000<br/>Summary: A chef from &quot;Sushi Sho&quot; offers a tranquil sushi dining experience.<br/>Signature cues: Sushi<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244448/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
