      <name>Simplicité</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Simplicité</strong><br/>Tokyo / Ebisunishi<br/>Address:  1F, 2-17-13 , Ebisunishi, Shibuya-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: 6-minute walk from Tokyu Toyoko Line Daikanyama Station<br/>Cuisine: French<br/>Reservation: Reservation request<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 25,410 - 25,410<br/>Lunch range: $$$ JPY 10k-20k<br/>Lunch: JPY 12,705 - 12,705<br/>Child policy: Children are welcome but must be able to eat the same course as an adult<br/>Summary: The umami (flavor) of &quot;French aged fish&quot;, sourced directly from its place of production, is brought out by clever use of technology.<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244281/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
