    <Placemark>
      <name>Kagurazaka MARUTOMI</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<strong>Kagurazaka MARUTOMI</strong><br/>Tokyo / Fukuromachi<br/>Address: Claire Kagurazaka 14（クレール神楽坂14）, 1st floor, 3-4, Fukuromachi, Shinjuku-ku, Tokyo<br/>Nearest: 4 min walk from Ushigome-Kagurazaka Station on the Oedo Line.; 8 minutes from Iidabashi Station.; 6 minutes from Kagurazaka Station on the Tozai Line.<br/>Cuisine: Japanese, Kaiseki, Washoku<br/>Reservation: Book Instantly<br/>Dinner range: $$$$ JPY 20k-30k<br/>Dinner: JPY 27,500 - 27,500<br/>Summary: A world gourmet guide awarded, starred restaurant where you can enjoy a variety of sumptious seasonal dishes, including the owner-chef&#x27;s speciality Iwate beef course.<br/>Known for: World gourmet guide, Seasonal cooking<br/>Signature cues: Kaiseki<br/><a href="https://pocket-concierge.jp/en/restaurants/244105/?extlink=va-jp-ICS-GMS_LP_en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pocket Concierge</a><br/>Source venue coordinates from Pocket Concierge.]]></description>
